sun
============
1. File List

   fema/		fema lib
   boost/ 		boost lib
   lib/			ssl, crypto, soil, fema lib
   bin/			
   bin/sun		fema load test program
   bin/sun.cfg		sun config file
   bin/log.cfg		log config file
   bin/env.sh		execute environment setup
   bin/traderflow	store the flow files for fema

2. Flow Diagram

   sun				fema_server
   	ReqOrderInsert
    -------------------------->

	OnRspOrderInsert
    <-------------------------

	OnRtnOrder
    <-------------------------

	ReqOrderAction
    ------------------------->

	OnRspOrderAction
    <------------------------

	OnRtnOrder
    <-------------------------



3. Deployment

   a) create fema_test user
      > sudo useradd -m fema_test

   b) put the fema_load.tar.gz to the fema_test home path
   
   c) extract the fema_load.tar.gz
      > tar zxvf fema_load.tar.gz

4. Run
     
   a) goto the bin path
   > cd fema_load/bin

   b) setup the execute env
   > source env.sh

   c) check the help
   > ./sun --help

   Command line options:
   -v [ --version ]               print version string
   --help                         produce help message
   -c [ --config ] arg (=sun.cfg) name of a file of a configuration.
   --load_test                    load test
   --query_account                query account
   --query_order                  query order
   --just_order                   just order
   --order_cancel order_sysid     order cancel

   d) update the sun.cfg

   e) execute the load test
   > ./sun

   f) check the statistic file info, the 'xxx' just is the stat_prefix in sun.cfg
   > more xxx_order.dat
   > more xxx_orader_action.dat